headline: Archer Aviation Stock (ACHR) Soars on Strong Q1 and Upcoming UAE Launch
summary: Archer Aviation (ACHR) has seen its stock jump over 47% this week since it delivered a commanding performance in the first quarter of 2025, beating earnings expectations while positioning itself for the historic milestone of becoming one of the first companies to launch commercial electric air taxi operations with its eVTOL aircraft. The results showcase a company successfully navigating the complex path from aviation startup to operational reality. The future of flying cars is finally here. I h
